    Enum defining the individual features available on a device

    Ideally the name of the Feature would have alignment with the name of the Event. For example, the Event name for EVENT_GESTURE_TAP implies that it's part of the Feature FEATURE_SENSOR_GESTURES due to "SENSOR_GESTURES" being present in both
